org.locationtech.geowave.core.ingest.hdfs.mapreduce

Class AbstractMapReduceIngest<T extends Persistable & DataAdapterProvider<?>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configured
      • org.locationtech.geowave.core.ingest.hdfs.mapreduce.AbstractMapReduceIngest<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of map-reduce ingest plugin that can be persisted to the map-reduce job configuration and used by the mapper and/or reducer to ingest data
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configurable, org.apache.hadoop.util.Tool
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IngestWithMapperJobRunner, IngestWithReducerJobRunner

    public abstract class AbstractMapReduceIngest<T extends Persistable & DataAdapterProvider<?>>
extends org.apache.hadoop.conf.Configured
implements org.apache.hadoop.util.Tool
    This class can be sub-classed to run map-reduce jobs within the ingest framework using plugins provided by types that are discovered through SPI.
